{
  "texts": [
    "By only considering the literature published in journals, we implicitly condition on Published.",
    "On the path Open data → Published ← Rigour → Reproducibility, Published acts as a collider.",
    "As discussed in Section II, conditioning on a collider can bias our estimates.",
    "We show the level of Reproducibility for Open data when considering only research that is Published in Open data than without Open data.",
    "This is rather counterintuitive, since the causal effect of Open data on Reproducibility is in fact positive in our model."
  ]
}